/* Table: busi_product */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_product (
ProID int identity(10000,1),
ShopID int not null,
BrandID int not null,
CID int not null,
PicUrl varchar(500) not null,
PriceD decimal(10,2) not null,
PriceR decimal(10,2) not null,
PriceJ decimal(10,2) not null,
Property int not null,
ExType int not null,
Status int not null,
Name varchar(200) null,
SaltNum7 int null,
SaltNum30 int null,
SaltNum int null,
EnTitle varchar(500) null,
JpTitle varchar(500) null,
"Desc" varchar(2000) null,
StockNum int not null,
YWeight int null,
SWeight int null,
SupplierID int not null,
Url varchar(500) null,
Model varchar(20) null,
Size varchar(50) null,
Code varchar(50) null,
Tag varchar(200) null,
DevePeople varchar(200) null,
BCode varchar(200) null,
Spec nvarchar(200) null,
BPrinc decimal(10,2) null,
PicLoc varchar(300) null,
Quality int null,
UpdateTime datetime not null default getdate(),
IsDel bit not null default 0,
AppTime datetime not null default getdate(),
constraint PK_BUSI_PRODUCT primary key (ProID)
)
go
